text: Aman Lal Modi (born 21 September, 1985) is a Nepalese politician and social worker who represents Morang 4 in the House of Representatives. He was also a member of the 2nd Nepalese Constituent Assembly, having been elected from the Unified CPN (Maoist) party. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
